  "special": {
    "title": "It's closer than you think! (no it isn't)",
    "description": "Fires a fixed sideways figure-eight. Effectively no ammo consumption and no normal reloads, with a fixed magazine of 1. Reduced damage and fire rate. Aiming down sights tightens the pattern but does not remove it."
  },
  "notes": "It only drops in True Vault Hunter Mode and above, and it still needs at least one pistol round in reserve to fire. Its fixed magazine lets 0ne Sh0t 0ne Kill apply to every shot. It is especially strong with Gaige because it supports Close Enough, Cooking Up Trouble, and safe Anarchy stacking without accidental reloads, though Discord cannot trigger from it. Some variants can add an extra bullet, and every eighth shot is perfectly accurate at the center of the pattern. If the magazine is reduced to zero, it becomes unusable.",
